title: Time of the Witch
subTitle: A small town in Arizona. The Townspeople are terrified. They are convinced that Aliens will invade soon. The priest blames the townspeople for turning their backs on God. A young woman, Sophia, hears voices telling her she must save everyone. She heals Richard, a broken and suicidal man. When she rejects him, he accuses her of drugging and seducing him. The townspeople accuse her of witchcraft, of ruining a respectable man. They blame her for all their troubles.
